[h3 id=YetThereWasSomethingThatStillBuggedMeABitWhenJudgingTheRun 
	"Yet, there was something that still bugged me a bit when judging the run:
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Strictly looking at this submission's time, it's 
	[em 
		"faster
	]em
	" than the published baseline run noted above.  This seemed odd to me, as I would have assumed a run restricted to playing with only the Hero would be 
	[em 
		"slower
	]em
	" than a run using the maximum (or as many as desired) party members.  So I had to do some more investigation.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Bear with me.  The following is somewhat convoluted, contains some (freely admitted) assumptions, and the estimations may not be super accurate; but I still hope the conclusion of it all will make sense.
	$LF
