[div class=p 
	"Looking at these timing differences we can infer a few things.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Regardless of goal, Japanese is the purely faster language choice.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" For either party option, the difference in switching from Japanese to English yields a roughly 21% longer run than the Japanese run.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" For either language, the difference in switching from "hero only" to "any %" yields a roughly 30% shorter run than the "hero only" run.
		$LF
	]li
