[div class=p 
	"So now with these estimated/theorized times we can look at the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=current English any%|href=/3702M)
	" publication's time compared to what we would expect.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"At 1,313,897 frames (6:06:01.94), the current publication is just barely faster than a theorized "hero only (English)" run.  Based on the above (admittedly theoretical) calculations, I would expect an English "any %" run should be possible closer to 945,609 frames (04:22:40) which is much shorter than the current publication.
	$LF
